Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:24.06,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,妳嘟著嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:30.95,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,表情裡看出了小算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:35.95,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,因為那份若即若離
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:46.13,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,被妳藏到了口袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:53.09,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,回憶是黑白照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:58.31,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,為它添上顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:06.86,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,再一次來到我的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.07,Ending Theme-CN,,0,0,0,,我五彩斑斕的寶貝兒女
